    {"type":"text","id":"artifact_plan_snip_t","x":98,"y":1392,"width":728,"height":205,"text":"Plan contract evidence\nRequired sections in plan.md template\n- Branch Setup (derive feat/<NNN>-<feature> from plan filename)\n- Implementation Plan (checkboxes updated live)\n- Intent Lock per phase: source refs, Must, Must Not, acceptance gates\n- Required Tests and Gates\n- Definition of Visible Done\n- Execution Report (append commands + outcomes)","originalText":"Plan contract evidence\nRequired sections in plan.md template\n- Branch Setup (derive feat/<NNN>-<feature> from plan filename)\n- Implementation Plan (checkboxes updated live)\n- Intent Lock per phase: source refs, Must, Must Not, acceptance gates\n- Required Tests and Gates\n- Definition of Visible Done\n- Execution Report (append commands + outcomes)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#2ECC71","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":504031,"version":1,"versionNonce":504131,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

