    {"type":"text","id":"artifact_validate_snip_t","x":890,"y":1392,"width":696,"height":205,"text":"Validation contract evidence (validate.md)\nLevel 1 fast loop\njust lint | just format-check | just types | just docs-check | just test\n\nLevel 2 final gate\njust quality && just test\n\nFailure policy\nfix root cause -> rerun failed command -> proceed on pass only\nWarning policy\ntreat warnings as actionable; document any unavoidable residual warnings","originalText":"Validation contract evidence (validate.md)\nLevel 1 fast loop\njust lint | just format-check | just types | just docs-check | just test\n\nLevel 2 final gate\njust quality && just test\n\nFailure policy\nfix root cause -> rerun failed command -> proceed on pass only\nWarning policy\ntreat warnings as actionable; document any unavoidable residual warnings","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#2ECC71","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":504033,"version":1,"versionNonce":504133,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25}
